{"tid":1148551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美媒記者：劉鶴於談判中途離席  表示他無法做任何事 要由元首決定","createTime":"2019-05-10T14:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T16:21:17.000Z","uid":144372,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b5d1f3b69123c58bd674e589dfa65990fa6e62","tid":1148551,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/News.aspx?NewsID=NOW.940849&amp;NewsType=&amp;NewsSource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3DNOW.940849%26NewsType%3D%26NewsSource%3DHK6&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=1c065d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/News.aspx?NewsID=NOW.940849&amp;NewsType=&amp;NewsSource=HK6</a><br />\n<br />\n霍士財經網》(Fox Business Network)記者Edward Lawrence在社交平台Twitter發表片段，指中國國務院副總理劉鶴昨晚(9日)與美國貿易代表萊特希澤及美國財長努欽進行工作晚餐期間中途離席。他亦引述消息稱，劉鶴向萊特希澤及努欽表示，他已不能做任何事，要由中美元首進行商討。(fc/da)~<br />\n<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=bcebe774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"0be730264bd1c8bac6b49f8f29f98d671b7a05b3","tid":1148551,"uid":78971,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國大露餡"},{"pid":"5a33f3a79e6d132a3c5